INSERT INTO `blog_article` VALUES (9, 'Webpack 最佳实践总结(一) ', '好久没写文章，这次预计会带来3篇的 Webpack 系列文章，将会在这几天内更新完(已更新完)。', '<p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 好久没写文章，这次预计会带来3篇的 Webpack 系列文章，<del style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">将会在这几天内更新完</del>(已更新完)。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关于基础知识部分，我之前写过一篇<a href=\"https://www.linpx.com/p/webpack-basic-tutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">《webpack2基础教程》</a>，足够入门了，不再多说。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/webpack/webpack-3-official-release-15fd2dd8f07b\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">Webpack3</a> 自今年6月20日正式发布而来，给我们带来<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Scope Hoisting</code>和<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Magic Comments</code>两大功能，<del style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">可惜不在这次系列文章内容范畴里</del>(食言了)，而本次文章的主要内容是从项目中总结得到，当然也看了很多别人写的文章，是可以被应用到生产中。这次主要介绍三个方面，分别是压缩 JavaScript 和 CSS、配置环境变量、ES 模块机制带来的Tree-shaking。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">假设我们有一个前端开发需求，这个需求有点特别，不是业务上的需求，而是要求减少文件的大小。可知这个需求算是性能优化上范畴，减少文件大小，加速网络传输，缩短网页加载时间，增加用户体验，提高用户满意度。这是一个正向结果，得干~</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></p><h3 id=\"directory060799749011356141\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2em; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; left: -15px; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">压缩 JavaScrip</span></h3><p><br></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这里不得不提一下 Google 的 <a href=\"https://github.com/google/closure-compiler\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">Closure Compiler</a>，一款可以让 JavaScript 下载与执行更快的工具，它的做法是执行一些\"焦土\"(scorched-earth)优化策略，它将函数展开，重写变量名，过滤多余代码，删除从不会调用的函数，从而生成可能是最优化的代码。如下</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">优化前</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">function map(array, iteratee) {\r\n  let index = -1\r\n  const length = array == null ? 0 : array.length\r\n  const result = new Array(length)\r\n\r\n  while (++index &lt; length) {\r\n    result[index] = iteratee(array[index], index, array)\r\n  }\r\n  return result\r\n}</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">优化后</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">function map(n,e){let r=-1;for(const i=null==n?0:n.length,t=Array(i);++r&lt;i;)t[r]=e(n[r],r,b);return t}</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对比发现优化效果极好，使用 <a href=\"https://github.com/mishoo/UglifyJS2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">UglifyJS</a> 一样可以达到相同的优化效果。由于 Webpack 内置这款插件，可以直接使用，配置如下</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// webpack.config.js\r\nconst webpack = require(\'webpack\');\r\n\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  plugins: [\r\n    new webpack.optimize.UglifyJsPlugin()\r\n  ]\r\n};</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用该插件优化前后的对比结果如下说明：</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">假设我们有一段代码，如下：</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// comments.js\r\nimport \'./comments.css\';\r\nexport function render(data, target) {\r\n    console.log(\'Rendered!\');\r\n}</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px