0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外我还写过 Webpack 跟 Less 和 Sass 的配置教程，具体看：<a href=\"https://www.linpx.com/p/webpack2-and-less-tutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">here1</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linpx.com/p/webpack2-and-sass-setup-tutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">here2</a><br></span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><br><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h3 id=\"directory060799749011356143\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2em; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; left: -15px; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">配置环境变量</span></h3><p><br></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">将<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NODE_ENV</code>设置为<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">production</code>也能帮助减少前端项目大小</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NODE_ENV</code>通常作为环境变量被各种js框架或库作为判断条件去作为哪种执行模式，如开发模式或是生产模式，这些框架或者库根据<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NODE_ENV</code>的值去表现对应的行为。例如，当处于开发模式时，React 会做额外的检测和打印警告：</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// …\r\nif (process.env.NODE_ENV !== \'production\') {\r\n  validateTypeDef(Constructor, propTypes, \'prop\');\r\n}\r\n// …</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果要打包构建项目到生产环境中，最好可以告诉项目中的框架或库当前的环境变量是生产环境。对于适用于 Node.js 的库来说，直接配置<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NODE_ENV</code>为<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">production</code>即可，但对于 Web 端来说，可以使用 Webpack 自带的插件实现对<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">process.env.NODE_ENV</code>的设置，如下</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// webpack.config.js\r\nconst webpack = require(\'webpack\');\r\n\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  plugins: {\r\n    new webpack.DefinePlugin({\r\n      \'process.env.NODE_ENV\': JSON.stringify(\'production\')\r\n    })\r\n  }\r\n};</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/plugins/define-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">DefinePlugin</a> 允许我们创建全局变量，同时这些变量会作用于webpack的打包编译期内。它会代替所有的<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">process.env.NODE_ENV</code>实例的值为<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\"production\"</code>，从而使 UglifyJS 知道那些判断表达式总是错误的，从而删除相关代码，进一步压缩打包文件</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></p><h3 id=\"directory060799749011356144\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2em; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; left: -15px; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">ECMAScript模块机制</span></h3><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">项目中使用 ECMAScript 的<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">import</code>、<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">export</code>，Webpack 通过 tree-shaking 也能通过打包有用的代码，进一步减少大小。 Tree-shaking 可以检查整个打包依赖树，找到使用的部分。所以如果使用 ECMAScript 模块机制，Webpack 会去掉无用的代码，如下:</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">假设写了两个文件，但只使用了其中一个文件</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// comments.js\r\nexport const commentRestEndpoint = \'/rest/comments\';\r\nexport const render = () =&gt; { return \'Rendered!\'; };\r\n\r\n// index.js\r\nimport { render } from \'./a.js\';\r\nrender();</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Webpack 知道<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">componentRestEndpoint</code>是没有被使用，打包文件也不会有该入口</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// bundle.js (part of)\r\n(function(module, __webpack_exports__, __webpack_require__) {\r\n  \"use strict\";\r\n  /* unused harmony export commentRestEndpoint */\r\n  /* harmony export */__webpack_exports__[\"b\"] = render;\r\n\r\n  var commentRestEndpoint = \'/rest/comments\';\r\n  var render = function () { return \'Rendered!\'; }\r\n})</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">UglifyJS 插件去掉无用部分</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// bundle.js (part of)\r\n(function(n,e){\"use strict\";e.b=r;var r=function(){return\"Rendered!\"}})</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果 JavaScript 框架或库使用了 ECMAScript 模块机制，那么 Tree-shaking 是对其也是有效滴</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">注意事项</strong></span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、 如果没有 UglifyJS ，tree-shaking 将不作用</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实际上，去掉无用的代码不是 Webpack 本身，而是 UglifyJS。Webpack 只是去掉 export 表达式使那些 exports 不再使用，从而可以在压缩的时候被去掉。因此，如果你打包的时候没有使用压缩，打包文件就不会变得更小</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、不要将 ES 模块机制编译为 CommonJS</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你使用了 <code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">babel-preset-env</code> 或 <code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">babel-preset-es2015</code>，就需要检查一下这些 preset 的配置了。默认情况下，它们都会ES 模块机制的语法特性重新编译为 CommonJS，如将 ES 的<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">import</code>和<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">export</code>编译为 CommonJS 的<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">require</code>和<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">module.exports</code>。我们可以使用 <code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">{ modules: false }</code> 禁止编译行为，如下：</span></p><pre style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto auto; border: 0px none; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; word-spacing: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\" style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 0px;\">// webpack.config.js\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  module: {\r\n    rules: [\r\n      {\r\n        test: /\\.js[x]$/,\r\n        use: [{\'babel-loader\', options: {\r\n          presets: [[\'es2015\', { modules: false }]]\r\n        }]\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n};</code></span></font></pre><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、在特殊条件下 Webpack 不会进行优化</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当你使用了<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">export * from \'file.js\'</code> 或者是 TypeScript，Webpack 是不会进行优化。这些特殊条件在代码中很难被发觉，也很难知道这些特殊条件的代码是否被修复，更多了解可以查看 <a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/webpack/issues/2867#issuecomment-247288543\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;\">here</a><br></span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><br><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h3 id=\"directory060799749011356145\" style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2em; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; left: -15px; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总结</span></h3><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Webpack 对前端项目优化有很多种，这里提供了四种技巧，分别是通过 UglifyJS 插件实现对 JavaScript 文件的压缩，css-loader 提供的压缩功能，配置<code style=\"border: 0px none; border-radius: 3px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">NODE_ENV</code>可以进一步去掉无用代码，tree-shaking帮助找到更多无用代码</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, SF UI Text, Arial, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, WenQuanYi Micro Hei, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">内容较多，大概就这样~</span></p><p><br></p>', '1', '2018-07-21 20:40:22', '2019-01-15 22:11:47', 34, 'true', '笔记', 3, 0, 'true', '');
